*Webflow is hiring a Freelance writer* :rocket:

*This is a freelance role.*

*What's the deal?* 

Webflow is looking for two freelancers to cover two different areas (or one talented one who can do both): 1) being able to write copy for landing pages about Webflow's use cases for different audiences (in-house web designers, freelance designers, agencies, marketers) and 2) can talk to visual developers about what they've built using Webflow and turn that into a story with some light technical details. Skills required include: interviewing, concise copywriting, interviewing, familiarity with design tools or no-code/visual development. Job can be remote anywhere in the world as long as you can do this type of work for a US-based company. 

*To apply, send an email to:* `<mailto:mischa@webflow.com|mischa@webflow.com>`
